{"tid":1025591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"反了反了，無線播沒有煙抽的日子","createTime":"2019-02-17T12:45:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-17T12:52:48.000Z","uid":166886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"22d640c8494fef777283299c0f639e034d318d7a","tid":1025591,"uid":166886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T12:45:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">作詞：王丹</span><br />\n作曲：張雨生<br />\n編曲：陳志遠<br />\n<br />\n沒有煙抽的日子 沒有煙抽的日子<br />\n我總不在你身旁<br />\n而我的心裡一直 以你為我的唯一的<br />\n唯一的一份希望<br />\n<br />\n天黑了 路無法延續到黎明<br />\n我的思念一條條鋪在<br />\n那個灰色小鎮的街頭<br />\n你們似乎不太喜歡沒有藍色的鴿子飛翔 啊～<br />\n<br />\n手裡沒有煙那就劃一根火柴吧<br />\n去抽你的無奈<br />\n去抽那永遠無法再來的一縷雨絲 喔～<br />\n<br />\n在你想起了我以後<br />\n又沒有煙抽的日子 喔～<br />\n<br />\n幾時播埋自由花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93e0bf6a04c5869044bb5e27b7c11c4890f17740","tid":1025591,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T12:52:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i7VzubQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi7VzubQ.png&h=4410c6e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GY35ARR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGY35ARR.png&h=821d2e11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vcgF9bZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvcgF9bZ.png&h=c9154b50&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}